  ('pukao-d0d1b9a2-moex-00072', 'pukao-d0d1b9a2', 'pukao-d0d1b9a2-moex-113-d35177eb', 'sub-pukao-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'essay', '甲公司某設備於X1年初以$100,000購置，採直線法計提列折舊，估計經
